form.official-title: To make technical corrections to Public Law 110–229 to reflect the renaming of the Bainbridge Island Japanese American Exclusion Memorial, and for other purposes.

section.header: Bainbridge Island Japanese American Exclusion Memorial
section.text: Section 313 of the Consolidated Natural Resources Act of 2008 (Public Law 110–229) is amended as follows:

paragraph.text: In the heading of subsection (b), by striking Japanese American Memorial and inserting Japanese American Exclusion Memorial.
In the heading of subsection (c)(5)(C), by striking Japanese American Memorial and inserting Japanese American Exclusion Memorial.
In subsection (c)(5)(C), by striking Japanese American Memorial and inserting Japanese American Exclusion Memorial.
